An early morning fire outbreak, on Wednesday, has razed some shops at the Apongbon Under Bridge Market in Lagos. Although details of the fire incident and its cause were still sketchy, it was gathered that it started early Wednesday morning at around 4am. As at the time of filing this report, the fire was still raging. Some vehicles parked under the bridge were also gutted by the fire which has enveloped a large section of the bridge. Officials of the Federal and Lagos State Fire Service have arrived the scene trying to put out the fire. Details Laterâ€¦.